      <title>Freshworks 調降年度營收預期、執行長換屆後股價暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/freshworks-plunges-after-cutting-annual-revenue-forecast-ceo-transition-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CRM 軟體製造商 Freshworks 下調全年營收預期並任命了新執行長後，其股價週四在盤前交易中暴跌近 30%。]]></description>
