      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 11:16:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技巨頭的市值因人工智慧疑慮和高利率而下降； Alphabet、特斯拉上漲</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/global-markets-marketcap-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受人工智慧熱情減弱和央行降息預期減弱的影響，頂級科技巨頭市值在 4 月大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/global-markets-marketcap-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 10:13:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
