      <title>由於電動車銷售成長放緩，晶片製造商 Wolfspeed 預測季度收入低於預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chipmaker-wolfspeed-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-below-estimates-ev-sales-growth-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[晶片製造商 Wolfspeed 週三預測本季營收低於預期，原因是汽車製造商因電動車銷售成長慢於預期而面臨高庫存水準。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chipmaker-wolfspeed-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-below-estimates-ev-sales-growth-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 21:23:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由於旗艦智慧型手機市場疲軟，Qorvo 預測季度業績低於預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/qorvo-forecasts-quarterly-results-below-estimates-weak-flagship-smartphone-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[無線連接晶片製造商 Qorvo 週三預測第一季營收和利潤低於華爾街預期，預計旗艦智慧型手機市場需求疲軟，導致其股價在售後交易中下跌超過 11%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/qorvo-forecasts-quarterly-results-below-estimates-weak-flagship-smartphone-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 21:21:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由於可自由支配需求下降，Etsy 未能實現第一季銷售和利潤預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/etsy-misses-first-quarter-sales-profit-estimates-lower-discretionary-demand-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週三，Etsy 未能達到華爾街對第一季商品銷售總額 (GMS) 和利潤的預期，原因是其線上市場對其手工製品和個人化禮品的需求下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/etsy-misses-first-quarter-sales-profit-estimates-lower-discretionary-demand-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 20:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由於消費者支出仍然緊張，eBay 預測第二季度收入低於預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/ebay-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-below-expectations-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[電子商務公司 eBay 週三預測第二季營收低於華爾街預期，原因是收藏品和汽車零件等主要產品類別的需求降溫，導致其股價在盤後交易中下跌 5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/ebay-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-below-expectations-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 20:10:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智慧推動中國晶片銷售，高通預測超乎預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-forecast-beats-estimates-ai-revives-smartphone-market-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高通週三預測的季度銷售額和調整後利潤高於華爾街預期，原因是向具有人工智慧功能的 Android 智慧型手機銷售了更多且價格更高的晶片。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-forecast-beats-estimates-ai-revives-smartphone-market-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 20:01:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
